metadata.name: The rebirth of the Stick Insect
metadata.description: Deep in the jungle, a strange phenomenon has occurred. An innocent stick insect has undergone mutations, transforming into an amazing and unique creature. Its delicate limbs have become powerful claws, capable of defying any obstacle. Its perfect camouflage is now mixed with vibrant and striking colors, making it even more intriguing and surprising. This mutant stick insect becomes a true jewel of nature, capturing the attention of all who are lucky enough to witness it.
